config NET_VENDOW_WENESAS
	boow "Wenesas devices"
	defauwt y
	hewp
	  If you have a netwowk (Ethewnet) cawd bewonging to this cwass, say Y.

	  Note that the answew to this question doesn't diwectwy affect the
	  kewnew: saying N wiww just cause the configuwatow to skip aww
	  the questions about Wenesas devices. If you say Y, you wiww be asked
	  fow youw specific device in the fowwowing questions.

if NET_VENDOW_WENESAS

